season_door.oil_explain_text:
Oil Application Guide:

1. After dispatch, reward drops will be boosted based on the type of oil applied.
Abundant Oil: Increases the quantity of Ancient Accessories dropped.
Mystic Oil: Increases the quantity of enhancement items dropped.
Bountiful Oil: Greatly increases the quantity of Ancient Accessories dropped.
Exalted Oil: Additionally drops a Selectable Ancient Accessory Set.
Transcendent Oil: Additionally drops a Selectable Ancient Accessory Set (+1 Level).
Mythic Oil: Additionally drops three Selectable Ancient Accessory Sets (+1 Level).

2. Oil application is only allowed after all waves are victorious; otherwise, your available oil uses remain unchanged.
season_door.new_result_text_1: Fought 3 battles with the current lineup.
season_door.new_result_text_2: Dispatch time  is determined by  the overall results of a simulated 3-battle assessment. After dispatch, oil is applied and rewards drop based on battle results until the time limit is reached or dispatch is manually canceled.
season_door.new_result_text_3: All battles were lost. Dispatch will not proceed.
